text: Over and Out is the fourth and final studio album by American post-hardcore band Tar, released in 1995 through Touch and Go Records. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ===Performers=== *John Mohr - Vocals, electric guitar *Mark Zablocki - Electric guitar, e-bow *Mike Greenlees - Drum set *Tom Zaluckyj - Electric bass guitar, electric guitar, vocals *Al Johnson - Vocals on "Known Anomalies" ===Production=== *Bob Weston - Recording engineering *Steve Albini - Recording engineering ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 albums
title: Over and Out (Tar album)
